snippet.title: Demetrios - The BIG Cynical Adventure - Launch Trailer | PS Vita
snippet.description:
Adventure, Visual Novel and puzzles mixed with silly jokes. 10 hours of fun! http://www.demetriosgame.com Fully optimized for PS Vita, this adventure is translated into 6 languages (English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Russian). Available November 15th, 2016! 

http://www.demetriosgame.com/
